channel.title: Bizarre Problem, Only Google works
channel.description:
Hey, the problem started to happen, like .5h ago, i was connected to the internet through wifi, and i was only able to access google, i can search through google, check gmail etc, but i can't leave google. Example if i search something and click on the link, it won't work.
Do you know what's the problem behind it?
p.s, it works fine after i disabled TCP/IPv6 on my wireless setting.
